- `pnpm --filter @hanzi/server typecheck` — OK
- `pnpm --filter @hanzi/web typecheck` — OK
- `pnpm --filter @hanzi/shared build` — OK
- `pnpm --filter @hanzi/server build` — OK
- `pnpm --filter @hanzi/web build` — OK (vite + PWA sw)
